    <item>
      <title>南非财政部长超过预算的民主联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/south-africa-finance-chief-slams-democratic-alliance-over-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长伊诺克·戈登瓦纳（Enoch Godongwana）批评民主联盟对反对关键预算立法的计划，并建议如果该党反对，它应该放弃国家联合政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/south-africa-finance-chief-slams-democratic-alliance-over-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 15:23:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尔西（Kalshi）的顶级律师退出成为SEC的Doge团队的领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/kalshi-s-top-lawyer-quits-to-become-leader-of-doge-team-at-sec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，衍生品交易所Kalshi Inc.的前首席监管官Eliezer Mishory正在领导美国证券交易委员会的总督团队。]]></description>
