    <item>
      <title>美国敦促访问南非商业领袖平衡贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-urges-visiting-south-africa-business-leaders-to-balance-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据来自非洲大陆最大的经济体的商业和劳工领袖说，南非和美国之间的破碎关系取决于平衡的贸易，他们与华盛顿的美国政客会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-urges-visiting-south-africa-business-leaders-to-balance-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 14:56:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
